{"tid":392354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教大閉路電視畫面截圖遭公開    譚凱邦向私隱公署投訴","createTime":"2017-09-08T12:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T14:40:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":158,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e30d118ca370839e4a54ecdf89c1c69dd2d088e","tid":392354,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"香港電台-港聞<br />\n&bull;\t2017年9月8日 下午7:32<br />\n<br />\n教育大學民主牆早前有人貼上奚落教育局副局長蔡若蓮喪子的字句，下午有傳媒聲稱有讀者提供閉路電視畫面截圖，將得到的畫面截圖公開，見到兩名被遮蔽眼睛的男子。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣區議員譚凱邦表示，已向個人資料私隱專員公署投訴。他認為，提供截圖的人以及公開截圖的媒體，均侵犯了個人私隱。他指出，以不法得來的閉路電視畫面截圖，會引導公眾作公開批鬥。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，已要求個人資料私隱專員公署立即調查教大有否允許將畫面截圖交予媒體公開、要求署方交代教大是否已違反《閉路電視監察措施指引》及《個人資料（私隱）條例》。"},{"pid":"c2d80192e62b7314e1df121d8705e66b990e02dd","tid":392354,"uid":25408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"教畜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e1e28761e159ef93dd655f07183084dd91c8fd","tid":392354,"uid":1082,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"條友又幾識撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954403b4023bd346788214546cd5bcf3be0879e5","tid":392354,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友又幾識撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e31a89be74b63f2f154b7a026488eaa5bb10cc","tid":392354,"uid":3860,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T12:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友又幾識撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有人做好過冇人做<br />\n<img src=\"/a